30|$|To assess teachers’ writing {{assessment}} {{ability and}} their WCF strategies, we designed a task. Teachers {{were required to}} assess two writing pieces, giving a score based on the IELTS writing assessment criteria. We provided the IELTS band descriptors as an appendix to all teachers. The writing samples provided by two examinees in the two <b>writing</b> <b>tasks</b> which teachers {{in the first stage}} of the study had completed were adopted from Cambridge IELTS 11 (General Module), a letter writing and an essay <b>writing</b> <b>tasks.</b> The samples adopted had been assessed by the IELTS examiners and the scores of 4.5 and 6.5 were given to the letter and essay <b>writing</b> <b>tasks,</b> respectively.|$|R
