50|$|Writing {{assessment}} {{refers to}} an area of study that contains theories and practices that guide the evaluation of a writer's performance or potential through a <b>writing</b> <b>task.</b> Writing assessment {{can be considered a}} combination of scholarship from composition studies and measurement theory within educational assessment. Writing assessment can also refer to the technologies and practices used to evaluate student writing and learning.|$|E
